<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Fuel Finder Pro UK Privacy Policy</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #0a84ff;
      --text: #1c1c1e;
      --secondary: #6e6e73;
      --background: #f5f5f7;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --border: #e5e5ea;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text",
        "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
      background: var(--background);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 42px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .effective-date {
      color: var(--secondary);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    h3 {
      margin-top: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: #2c2c2e;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 0 0 22px 20px;
      padding: 0;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 48px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--secondary);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      body {
        padding: 20px 14px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 28px 22px;
        border-radius: 22px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">

      <h1>Privacy Policy for Fuel Finder Pro UK</h1>

      <div class="effective-date">
        Effective Date: 9 May 2026
      </div>

      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>Fuel Finder Pro UK</strong> (“Fuel Finder Pro UK”, “we”, “our”, or “us”).
      </p>

      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how Fuel Finder Pro UK collects, uses, and protects information when you use the application on iPhone and CarPlay-enabled devices.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Location Information</h3>

      <p>
        Fuel Finder Pro UK uses your device location to:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>show nearby fuel stations</li>
        <li>calculate distance and route information</li>
        <li>improve station sorting accuracy</li>
        <li>support navigation features</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Location data is only accessed with your permission through Apple’s iOS permission system.
      </p>

      <p>
        We do not continuously track your location in the background unless explicitly permitted by iOS and required for app functionality.
      </p>

      <h3>Usage Information</h3>

      <p>
        The app may collect limited anonymous diagnostic and performance information, including:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>app crashes</li>
        <li>loading performance</li>
        <li>API/network errors</li>
        <li>device compatibility information</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        This information is used solely to improve app reliability and performance.
      </p>

      <h3>Fuel Pricing &amp; Station Data</h3>

      <p>
        Fuel Finder Pro UK uses publicly available UK fuel pricing and station information, including data provided through the UK fuel price transparency scheme and associated station data providers.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Advertising</h2>

      <p>
        Fuel Finder Pro UK may display advertisements within the app.
      </p>

      <p>
        Advertising providers may collect limited technical information such as:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>device type</li>
        <li>advertising identifiers</li>
        <li>approximate location</li>
        <li>app interaction data</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        This information may be used to provide relevant advertising and measure advertising performance.
      </p>

      <p>
        Advertising services may include:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Google AdMob</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        You can control advertising permissions through your iOS privacy settings.
      </p>

      <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>

      <p>
        We use collected information to:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>provide nearby fuel station results</li>
        <li>improve fuel price accuracy</li>
        <li>maintain app functionality</li>
        <li>improve performance and reliability</li>
        <li>support navigation and routing features</li>
        <li>monitor service stability and errors</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        We do not sell personal information to third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Data Storage</h2>

      <p>
        Most app preferences are stored locally on your device.
      </p>

      <p>
        We aim to minimise the amount of personal data collected and retained.
      </p>

      <p>
        Some technical information may be temporarily processed through third-party infrastructure required for app operation, including map services, fuel data services, analytics, and advertising providers.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>

      <p>
        Fuel Finder Pro UK may rely on third-party services including:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Apple Maps</li>
        <li>Google Maps</li>
        <li>Waze</li>
        <li>Google AdMob</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        These services operate under their own privacy policies and terms.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Your Choices</h2>

      <p>
        You can:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>disable location access in iOS Settings</li>
        <li>manage advertising permissions in iOS Privacy settings</li>
        <li>uninstall the app at any time</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Some features may not function correctly without location access.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Children’s Privacy</h2>

      <p>
        Fuel Finder Pro UK is not directed toward children under 13 years of age.
      </p>

      <p>
        We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>

      <p>
        We take reasonable measures to help protect information and maintain app security. However, no electronic transmission or storage system can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy periodically.
      </p>

      <p>
        Updated versions will be posted with a revised effective date.
      </p>

      <p>
        Continued use of the app after changes become effective constitutes acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>

      <p>
        For privacy-related questions or requests, contact:
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Fuel Finder Pro UK Support</strong><br />
        Email: FuelFinderProUK@gmail.com
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        © 2026 Fuel Finder Pro UK. All rights reserved.
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
